    "leads_by_channel_mtd": "real per-channel counts, but facility_day_leadsource only started 2026-07-09 \u2014 as of 2026-07-10 it covers a partial window, not the full MTD leads_total figure; fills out day by day.",
    "ad_spend_month": "reflects 2026-06, the latest CLOSED month \u2014 ad spend refreshes monthly at month-close, not on this twice-daily cadence.",
    "rent_per_sqft": "null everywhere: the verbatim Nectar rate field is not captured into facility_day, and a MTD-sum-based proxy would drift upward through the month rather than hold steady like a real rate \u2014 rejected as misleading, not computed."
